{"id":37,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":37,"title":"Chapter 34: Helaman and the 2,000 Young Warriors","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 34"],["h1","Helaman and the 2,000 Young Warriors"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p3"},"The people of Ammon had promised God that they would never fight again. They lived near the Nephites, and the Nephites protected them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/53.10-12"},"Alma 53:10–12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p5"},"When enemies of the people of Ammon attacked the Nephites, the people of Ammon wanted to break their promise and help the Nephites fight."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/53.13"},"Alma 53:13"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p7"},"Helaman and the other Nephite leaders did not want the people of Ammon to break their promise to God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/53.14-15"},"Alma 53:14–15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p9"},"The young sons of the people of Ammon had not made the promise. They wanted to help the Nephite army fight for freedom."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/53.16-17"},"Alma 53:16–17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p11"},"Two thousand of these young men chose to defend their country. They asked Helaman to be their leader."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/53.18-19"},"Alma 53:18–19"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p13"},"These young men were valiant, brave, and strong. They were also honest and trustworthy, and they kept the commandments of God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/53.20-21"},"Alma 53:20–21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p15"},"Helaman led his 2,000 young warriors into battle. He called them his sons, and they called him their father."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/53.22"},"Alma 53:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/56.46"},"Alma 56:46"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p17"},"Although the sons of Helaman had never fought, they were not afraid. Their mothers had taught them to have faith in God and to know that he would help them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/56.47"},"Alma 56:47"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p19"},"Helaman and his army fought several battles against the Lamanites. These young men obeyed all of Helaman’s orders."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/57.19-21"},"Alma 57:19–21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p21"},"They fought bravely and helped drive the enemy away. After the battle Helaman found that all his sons had been hurt but not one had been killed."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/57.22,25"},"Alma 57:22, 25"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_037_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p23"},"It was a miracle. Helaman was very happy. He knew that these young men had been protected because of their great faith in God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-34-helaman-and-the-2000-young-warriors.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/57.26-27"},"Alma 57:26–27"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
